{"schema":"allo-reading-book@1","slug":"151579-irigimani-weyisi-mirikani","title":"እርግማን ወይስ ምርቃን?","description":"What happens when it rains on a dry land after a really long period?","language":"Amharic","langCode":"am","isRtl":false,"level":"2","orientation":"landscape","authors":["Kebede Yimer"],"illustrators":["Marleen  Visser","Natalie  Propa","Silva Afonso"],"originalAuthors":[],"publisher":"African Storybook Initiative","license":"CC BY 4.0","licenseUrl":"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/","sourceId":"storyweaver","contentType":"story","source":{"id":"storyweaver","name":"StoryWeaver, Pratham Books","url":"https://storyweaver.org.in/en/stories/151579-irigimani-weyisi-mirikani"},"cover":{"card":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/202073/size3/92a6f08eb53b4808fed60e2115904137.jpg","large":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/202073/size6/92a6f08eb53b4808fed60e2115904137.jpg"},"audio":null,"pages":[{"n":1,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/201006/size6/37abde0b4ff1b0e47bfe8fd970560a5c.jpg","text":"ለብዙ ወራት፣ ሰማይ ደረቅ ሆነ፡፡ ታዋቂው ዝናብ አምጪ ሎሞንጊን ለአማልእክቱ ተናገረ፡፡ ሰዎች ከሱ መኖሪያ ቤት አካባቢ ተሰብስበው፣ የተስፋውን መልእክት በጭንቀት መጠባበቅ ጀመሩ።","words":null},{"n":2,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/201007/size6/f19bdc7059c16c03d86f4e1b99392c2e.jpg","text":"ዝናብ አምጪው ሲመጣ፣ ፈጣሪ ለሰዎቹ ቶሎ ዝናብ ሊሰጣቸው እንደሆነ አረጋገጠ፡፡ እህላቸውን መዝራት ይችላሉ፡፡","words":null},{"n":3,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/201008/size6/feb766483f6d2010e87f5df388b0f986.jpg","text":"እኛ ዝናቡን ስንጠባበቅ ልጆች ውጭ ላይ ይጫወቱ ነበር፡፡ ከዚያ ቀን በኋላ፣ በሩቅ ምስራቅ በኩል ትላልቅ ነጫጭ ደመናዎችን አየን። እነሱ የዝናብ ደመናዎች እንደሆኑም አውቅኩ።","words":null},{"n":4,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/201012/size6/6841b761f176716bf5acf0f5ff95417f.jpg","text":"ዝናብ አምጭው ምን እንደሚል ሕዝቡ ገና እያሰላሰለ ነበር፡፡ እማዬ ጮክ ብላ “እዛ ጋ! ደመናዎቹ አሁን እየጠቆሩ ነው፡፡ ወደ ውስጥ ግቡ” አለች፡፡","words":null},{"n":5,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/201013/size6/d9e8c7f70b7431e2b6ece05032cf69aa.jpg","text":"ዝናቡ እየተንዠቀዠቀ ወረደ፡፡","words":null},{"n":6,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/201014/size6/fb72511010bd5820d7efe26d86fb344f.jpg","text":"ዝናቡን ስንጠብቅ ቆየን! መጀመሪያ ተደሰትን፡፡ ዝናቡ ግን አላባራ አለ፡፡","words":null},{"n":7,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/201015/size6/ab18d81065b13648fbe43200bfce22ed.jpg","text":"በሁሉም ቦታ ውሃ ነበር፡፡ መደራችንን ከዋናው ሰፈር የሚያገናኘው ድልድይ በጎርፍ ተወስዷል፡፡","words":null},{"n":8,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/201016/size6/261cc6b4e1a7ca5746e16486e6c89426.jpg","text":"ቤቶች በጎርፍ ተወሰዱ፡፡ ምን ነበር በረከቱ፣ ለእኛ ጥፋት ሆኖብናል፡፡","words":null},{"n":9,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/201017/size6/b820c4b7bed45ef87c6c63a8a65da7d6.jpg","text":"ሁሉም ሰው ለመዝራት ተዘጋጅቶ ነበር፡፡ አሁን ግን መዝራት አልቻለም፡፡ የመንደሬ ሰዎች ዝናብ ሲመኙ ነበር፡፡ አሁን ግን አይፈልጉትም፡፡ የምንሻገርበት ድልድይ የለም፡፡ ብዙ ሰዎች ቤት የላቸውም፡፡","words":null},{"n":10,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/201019/size6/4c8cf9e201c3aa5b4893c978847fee2e.jpg","text":"እናም፣ ሌላም ችግር ገጥሞናል! አዞዎች በሁሉም ቦታ ሲዋኙ አየን፡፡ ይህ ነገር ፈጽሞ ተከሥቶ አያውቅም፡፡ ግራ ገባን፡፡","words":null},{"n":11,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/201020/size6/75b36e64cc7ea35720d81aded0cf7ce4.jpg","text":"ሁሉም ሱቆች ከወንዙ ማዶ ስለነበሩ ወደ ሱቅ መሄድ አልቻልንም፡፡ ትምህርት ቤቶችም ከወንዙ ማዶ ስለነበሩ ሕጻናት ወደ ትምህርት ቤት መሄድ አልቻሉም፡፡","words":null},{"n":12,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/201021/size6/4abd2608c4175de2767f5a8509207545.jpg","text":"በረከት ምን መሆን ነበረበት፣ ለእኛ እርግማን ሆነብን፡፡ ዝናብ አምጪው ሎሞንጊንም እንደኛው ተበሳጭቷል፡፡ ብቸኛው ደስተኛ ከ8 ድመቶቹ ጋር ካፑስ ነበር፡፡","words":null}],"stats":{"pages":12,"words":190}}